features.feature: 亲爱的用户，本次更新包括，相机新增AI超清合影和外屏趣拍功能，YOYO 助理新增一句话多 APP 自动打车和一句话操控 APP 功能，新增 AI 帮写和 AI 生成 PPT 功能，推荐您进行更新。
• 新增 AI 超清合影功能。体验路径：相机 > 识别到合影场景 > 手动开启 AI 超清合影 > 拍照。 • 新增外屏趣拍功能。体验路径：相机 (展开态) > 打开外屏协同 > 选择要显示的趣拍素材。 • 优化相机拍照色彩、光影、清晰度等效果。 • 提升相机稳定性。
• 新增媒体的无极音量调节功能。

• 新增一键问屏支持深度思考功能。体验路径：在图片、文档查看页面唤醒 YOYO 后对屏幕内容进行提问，YOYO 识别屏幕中内容并进行回答。 • 新增 YOYO 助理一句话多 APP 自动打车功能。体验路径：唤醒 YOYO 后对 YOYO 说“帮我用滴滴和高德打车回家”，即可体验。 • 新增 YOYO 助理一句话操控APP功能。如对 YOYO 说“帮我打开拼多多我的订单”，即可体验。目前支持抖音、支付宝、拼多多、快手、淘宝、百度、美团等 APP。
• 新增 AI 生成 PPT 功能。体验路径：打开文档 (Word、PDF、TXT) > AI 文档 > 点击生成 PPT 或者在下方文本框输入生成 PPT 的要求，一句话生成 PPT。 • AI文档支持分栏显示，并接入Deepseek文档问答。体验路径：打开文档 (Word、PDF、PPT、TXT) > AI 文档 > 点击下方文本框进行提问。
• 新增 AI 帮写功能。支持在写文案、写点评等场景进行文案润色、总结和创作。体验路径：在支持的APP内长按文本输入框 > 点击 AI 帮写图标 > 选择帮写的类型和要求（具体支持的APP清单以实际体验为准）。
• 新增自动接听功能。设定响铃时间内未接听的电话，AI通话助理将自动帮您接听。体验路径：设置 > 荣耀 AI & YOYO > AI通话 > 自动接听。
• 新增自由屏功能。一屏三用，多应用同屏显示，看视频、网购、回消息一屏搞定。体验路径：桌面 > 底部 Dock > 快捷布局 > 选择分屏应用。
• 提升系统稳定性，让您的手机运行更稳定。
• 优化系统与部分第三方应用兼容性。 • 优化部分游戏场景的使用体验。
• 新增支持视频会议场景，开启后可在视频会议中对参会人员进行人脸伪造检测。体验路径：设置 > 安全 > 反诈防护 > AI换脸检测提醒 > 视频通话检测。
• 合入安卓 2025 年 6 月安全补丁，增强系统安全性。有关荣耀软件安全更新内容的信息，请访问荣耀官方网站 https://www.honor.com/cn/support/bulletin/2025/6
1. 本次更新不会删除您的用户数据，但仍建议您在更新前做好数据备份。 2. 更多精彩功能介绍，请访问“玩机技巧”应用。 3. 如果您在使用过程中遇到任何问题，请访问“我的荣耀”应用或访问荣耀官方服务网站 https://www.honor.com/cn/contact-us 寻求支持。

Dear user, this update enhances the Camera with AI Super Group Photo and the Cover screen fun shooting feature. YOYO Assistant allows you to book a ride with multiple apps using a simple voice command. You can also control apps with a simple voice command. Additionally, this release introduces AI writing and enables you to generate slides using AI. Update to enjoy the new features.

• AI Super Group Photo is available in Camera. Go to Camera, manually enable AI Super Group Photo after it recognizes a group photo scene, and then take a photo. • Camera also includes the Cover screen fun shooting feature. Open Camera when the device is unfolded, enable Cover screen collaboration and select the content to display on the cover screen. • Optimizes the Camera's photography effects, including color, clarity, light and shadow. • Improves the stability of Camera.
• You can now enjoy more precise volume adjustments for media playback.

• You can now get deeply analyzed results after inquiring about the screen content. When viewing an image or document, wake up YOYO and ask questions about the screen content. YOYO will analyze the content and provide answers. • YOYO Assistant enables automatic ride-hailing across multiple apps with a simple voice command. You can wake up YOYO and say "Book a ride home using Didi and Gaode" to try this feature. • YOYO Assistant also allows you to control apps with a simple voice command. For example, you can say "Open my orders on Pinduoduo" after waking up YOYO. It currently supports Douyin, Alipay, Pinduoduo, Kuaishou, Taobao, Baidu, Meituan and more.

• AI Doc enables you to generate slides using AI. Open a document (Word, PDF, TXT) and tap AI Doc, then tap Generate or enter the requirements for the slides in the text box below. • AI Document supports column display and integrates DeepSeek for Q&A. Open a document (Word, PDF, TXT, Slides) and tap AI Doc, then enter the questions about the doc in the text box below.

• AI writing helps to polish, summarize and create text in scenarios such as writing copy and reviews. Long press the input box in supported apps and tap AI writing icon, then select the type and requirements for the text to be generated (The list of supported apps is subject to actual experience).

• AI Call includes Auto-answer calls feature. AI Call Assistant can automatically answer a call if it is not answered within the set ringing time. Try it out by going to: Settings > Honor AI & YOYO > AI Call > Auto-answer calls.

• Free View allows you to use three apps at the same time. You can watch videos, shop, and reply to messages all on the same screen. Try it out by going to: Home screen > Bottom Dock > Quick layout > Select apps for split screen.
• Improves the system stability to make your device run more stably.
• Improves the system compatibility with some third-party apps. • Improves the user experience in some game scenarios.

• Video call detection is available in video conferences. Once enabled, face forgery detection can be performed on participants during video conferences. Try it out by going to: Settings > Security > Scam Protection > AI Deepfake Detection alert > Video call detection.

• Android security patch (Jun 2025) has been incorporated for system security. For more information about Honor Security updates, please visit our website https://www.honor.com/global/support/bulletin/2025/6

1. Installing this update will not affect your personal data, but it is still recommended to back up your data before updating. 2. Check out more information on product features in the Tips app. 3. If you encounter any problem during use, please get support by going to My Honor or visiting our website: https://www.honor.com/cn/contact-us.
